sentences: Rialda Karahasanović  (born 12 November 1992), known professionally as just Rialda, is a Bosnian pop recording artist, television personality and model.
Rialda Karahasanović was born in besieged Sarajevo on 12 November 1992 .
In 2012 she auditioned for the fifth season of the televised singing contest Zvijezda možeš biti ti
She competed again in the seventh season two years later and made it to the finals in May 2015.
Rialda's first single "Korak do dna" premiered 9 September 2015.
Her brother Ajdin is four years younger.
